name: Tourist Visa
description: Short-term visa for leisure travel, sightseeing, or visiting friends and family.

name: Business Visa
description: Issued for business meetings, conferences, or professional engagements.

name: Student Visa
description: Granted to students enrolling in educational institutions abroad.

name: Work Visa
description: Issued for foreign nationals taking up employment abroad.

name: Transit Visa
description: Required when passing through a country on the way to another destination.

name: Medical Visa
description: For those seeking medical treatment abroad.

name: Dependent Visa
description: Issued to family members of a person working or studying abroad.

name: Immigrant Visa
description: For individuals planning to permanently live in another country.

name: Diplomatic Visa
description: Issued to diplomats and government officials for official purposes.

name: Cultural Exchange Visa
description: For participants in cultural exchange programs and events.
